title: Good Food Made Simple Recalls Turkey and Pork Products Distributed Without the Opportunity for Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, July 31, 2015 Good Food Made Simple, a Wellesley, Mass., distributor, is recalling approximately 3,574 pounds of previously exported turkey sausage breakfast burritos and pork strips and turkey sausage breakfast bowls that were returned from Canada and were not presented for U.S. returned export...
